<p><strong>Narrowing the skills gap, one chapter at a time.</strong><br /><br /><span>Welcome to </span><strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/events/297852222/">Career Essentials in Generative AI</a></strong><span>. Let's begin.</span></p>
<p><span>This is the first of six weekly sprints. Once you complete each sprint you will receive a certificate to post to your LinkedIn profile. To demonstrate your commitment to begin this virtual self-study group opportunity, post a message<span> to </span><span><strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54055597/">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> to your fellow Boston PHP members. We have 24 learners who have signed up to begin the Generative AI journey.</span></span></p>
<p>Next, gain access to <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/learning/paths/career-essentials-in-generative-ai-by-microsoft-and-linkedin"><strong>Career Essentials in Generative AI by Microsoft and LinkedIn</strong></a>. This learning path has been made available for <strong>FREE</strong> for a limited time. Once you complete the first course (Sprint #1), post a message, along with a link to your certificate of completion in <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54055638">Generative AI: What is Generative AI?</a></strong> This will help us gauge progress among participants.</p>
<p>Finally, a complete list of weekly sprints can be found in <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54054010">Master Discussion List—Career Essentials in Generative AI</a></strong>. Post any questions you might have in the <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54055597/">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> discussion area.</p>
<p>Let's get artificial!</p>
